column1: Squirrel Census data collected by a team of dedicated volunteer Squirrel Surveyors, under directions from the Dept. of Data - NYC.
The Squirrel Census covered 24 parks in New York City.
Data was collected over a 1 year period; March 2020 to Febuary 2021.
